On the Raspberry Pi that will be used as the Pico development platform:

$ wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/raspberrypi/pico-setup/master/pico_setup.sh
$ chmod +x pico_setup.sh
$ ./pico_setup.sh
   On a Raspberry Pi Zero, the script will fail when it tries to run the
   "code" commands near the end.  Run the subsequent UART setup steps manually.
# systemctl reboot
